# Validate After Change

1. Run the narrow package tests for changed Go packages.
2. Run:

```bash
make test-main
make lint
make check-fmt
make validate
```

3. Run `make validate-versions`, `make generate`, `make test-images`, GPU
   integration, or Kubernetes e2e gates when the change touches those surfaces.
4. Record any skipped prerequisite-dependent gate with the reason.
